    public final class JLogMap
extends io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog.AbstractTerm
implements io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog.PrologMap
    A PrologTerm that maps PrologTerm keys to PrologTerm values. A map cannot contain duplicate keys. Each key can map to at most one value.

    1.1
    Author:
